# Web-UI dev loop (docs/WEB_UI.md): run with `hivemind Procfile.dev`.
# The daemon serves the API on 127.0.0.1:8666 (--web on); next dev serves
# the app on :3000 and proxies /api/* to the daemon (next.config.ts).
# Browse http://localhost:3000/app/ for live-reloading UI work.
daemon: just run --web on
web: cd web && pnpm dev
